  "solution": "f' = f₀ (1 ± v₍obs₎/v₍sound₎)\nGiven: f₀ = 1650 Hz, v₍obs₎ = 30.0 m/s, v₍sound₎ = 343 m/s\n\n(a) Moving toward the source (+):\nf' = 1650 Hz × (1 + 30.0/343)\nf' = 1650 Hz × (1 + 0.0875)\nf' = 1650 Hz × 1.0875\nf' = 1794 Hz ≈ 1.79 × 10³ Hz\n\n(b) Moving away from the source (−):\nf' = 1650 Hz × (1 − 30.0/343)\nf' = 1650 Hz × (1 − 0.0875)\nf' = 1650 Hz × 0.9125\nf' = 1506 Hz ≈ 1.51 × 10³ Hz"
